title: Native Foreigners
description: 'If Earth didn't want you, why would Cynthia?'In a distant future, Earth is no longer inhabitable. Humans had to run away to a planet called Cynthia. In this future, there is a woman named Jane who would do anything to find a cure for Dill. She goes on a journey with the help of Zeb, the taxi driver. After the long travel, she realizes things are much more complicated. Even planet Cynthia has its secrets. Jane will have to fight for the future while Zeb has to fight back the past.Native Foreigners is an action-packed science fiction thriller. It is loaded with guns, car chases, moments of humor, and the constant unknown.
author: Naylene Rondon
